metadata.name: Aqueryus
metadata.description:
Existence our game;
Searching for the unknown.
The competition remains constant-
And infinity shown.

Quantification our quest;
Existential exploration,
Perpetual perplexity-
Seeking summation.

This universal pursuit;
Binds our alliance,
As the masses compute-
A rhetorical science.

Undefined definition;
Of our social distinction'
In accordance to our dynamic
Sense of completion.

Our calculative crusade;
To analyze totality...
The proverbial we seek-
To our ambiguous mortality.

~Eskko
